rvice时都出现严重延迟\n2. **延迟倍数异常显著**：最高达到43倍延迟增长，表明服务性能严重恶化\n3. **数据库依赖问题**：productcatalogservice依赖TiDB，其性能问题可能源于数据库层面\n\n**建议后续调查方向**：\n- 检查TiDB数据库的性能指标和连接状态\n- 查看productcatalogservice的资源使用情况（CPU、内存）\n- 分析数据库查询语句的性能瓶颈\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "tidb-tikv is the root cause due to region_pending exhaustion (164.93% change rate) and productcatalogservice performance degradation caused by TiDB dependency"}
